OL,3,CForce expresses 'embarrassment' after
OL,4,Cdestroying Miners' Strike files, says
OL,5,CMP
OL,7,FAn MP says Northumbria Police
OL,8,F'expressed their professional
OL,9,Fembarrassment' when he met with the
OL,10,Fforce after it emerged they had
OL,11,Fdestroyed records relating to the
OL,12,FMiners' Strike and the 'Battle of
OL,13,FOrgreave'.
OL,15,FLabour's Ian Lavery, MP for Blyth &
OL,16,FAshington, posted on social media on
OL,17,FMonday (30 June) to say he had met
OL,18,Fwith representatives of the force.
