OL,3,CForce expresses 'embarrassment' after
OL,4,Cdestroying Miners' Strike files, says
OL,5,CMP
OL,7,FThe meeting follows the revelation
OL,8,Flast week that Northumbria Police had
OL,9,Fdisposed of two boxes containing data
OL,10,Frelating to its involvement in the
OL,11,Fyear-long strike of 1984 and violence
OL,12,Fthat erupted outside a coking plant in
OL,13,FSouth Yorkshire.
OL,15,FNorthumbria Police has confirmed it is
OL,16,Finvestigating the circumstances
OL,17,Fsurrounding its destruction.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
