OL,3,CForce expresses 'embarrassment' after
OL,4,Cdestroying Miners' Strike files, says
OL,5,CMP
OL,7,FWriting on X, Mr Lavery said" "On
OL,8,FFriday afternoon I met with senior
OL,9,Frepresentatives of Northumbria Police
OL,10,Fhaving written to them following the
OL,11,Fdiscovery that files relating to the
OL,12,Fpolicing of Orgreave and the Miners'
OL,13,FStrike had been destroyed last year.
OL,15,F"We spoke frankly about the mistrust
OL,16,Fthat this will have caused many in
OL,17,Fmining communities up and down the
OL,18,Fcountry, including those here in South
OL,19,FEast Northumberland and about the need
OL,20,Ffor the investigation into the matter
OL,21,Fto be transparent.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
