OL,3,CForce expresses 'embarrassment' after
OL,4,Cdestroying Miners' Strike files, says
OL,5,CMP
OL,7,F"The Police acknowledged this and
OL,8,Fexpressed their professional
OL,9,Fembarrassment that these documents had
OL,10,Fbeen destroyed and assured me that an
OL,11,Finvestigation had already begun to
OL,12,Funderstand the decision making behind
OL,13,Fthe actions.
OL,15,F"I look forward to further
OL,16,Fcorrespondence from them and in the
OL,17,Fmeantime will continue to press the
OL,18,Fgovernment for the inquiry into the
OL,19,Fpolicing of the full dispute that has
OL,20,Fbeen needed for so long."
